      var cb, data;
      if (params == null) {
        params = {};
      }
      if (fn == null) {
        fn = null;
      }
      if ('function' === typeof params) {

        params = {};
      }
      this.debug("Groups::all()");
      if (params.page == null) {
        params.page = 1;

        params.per_page = 100;

    };
